The Doxee Platform consists of multiple functionalities, or **services **(formerly referred to as "**portals**").

### Accessing a service
- â€‹Click ![](data:image/png;base64,) on the navigation bar to expand the menu.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

- Select the Doxee Platform service that you would like to access. The selected service's UI is opened in a new browser tab.

> Note

In the **Other **section of the menu, you may find links to custom services or external services, if available.

> Important

The services available to the user depend on the customer's permissions and licenses.
